I'm a student from a small college, and I am surprised by the amount of grade-related memes posted here. I always thought people at Cal-Berkley get straight As, or at least Bs, but I keep seeing memes making fun of their own GPAs, comparing their academics to other universities, comically saying how their semester grades are fucked, a failure, worth shit, etc. You guys need to have better grade self esteem fam.
